<c74object name='sp.databending' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Transform and distort descriptor streams
</digest>
    <description>Transform and distort descriptor streams.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.databending</o> object takes incoming descriptor data (descriptors, melbands, MFCCs, or sines) and apply various transformations and &#39;bends&#39;. The input can be lists or <o>buffer~</o> s and the same will be output.
</discussion>

